PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773245483
OL,3,CHelicopter from RNAS Culdrose arrives
OL,4,Cin Cyprus amid conflict in Middle East
OL,6,FA week ago, the RAF base at Akrotiri
OL,7,Fwas targeted by an Iranian drone
OL,8,Fattack.
OL,10,FThe helicopter which arrived on Monday
OL,11,Fis from 820 Naval Air Squadron and has
OL,12,Fa powerful radar and mission system
OL,13,Fwhich provides a defence against
OL,14,Faerial threats.
OL,16,FWith a crew of three, the aircraft can
OL,17,Ffly up to a mile in height and look
OL,18,F"over the horizon" to give an advance
OL,19,Fwarning of incoming drones or missiles.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
