OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773245483
OL,3,CHelicopter from RNAS Culdrose arrives
OL,4,Cin Cyprus amid conflict in Middle East
OL,6,FRoyal Navy Wildcat helicopters from
OL,7,F815 Naval Air Squadron, armed with air-
OL,8,Fto-air Martlet missiles, have already
OL,9,Fbeen sent to Cyprus. They were loaded
OL,10,Fonto an RAF C-17 transporter at RNAS
OL,11,FYeovilton for the flight to the
OL,12,FEastern Mediterranean island.
OL,14,FAlthough still to be tested in action,
OL,15,Fthe Wildcat-Martlet combination has
OL,16,Fproved successful repeatedly on test
OL,17,Franges with aircrew destroying aerial
OL,18,Fdrones.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773245483
OL,3,CHelicopter from RNAS Culdrose arrives
OL,4,Cin Cyprus amid conflict in Middle East
OL,6,FThe commanding officer of RNAS
OL,7,FCuldrose, Captain James Hall, said:
OL,8,F"We activated one of our ASaC aircraft
OL,9,Fto deploy immediately to provide an
OL,10,Fadditional layer of defence for our
OL,11,Fforces at Akrotiri.
OL,13,F"Our aircraft from Merlin Helicopter
OL,14,FForce are held at readiness to respond
OL,15,Fat short notice to any threat to UK
OL,16,Finterests.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773245483
OL,3,CHelicopter from RNAS Culdrose arrives
OL,4,Cin Cyprus amid conflict in Middle East
OL,6,F"820 Naval Air Squadron already has
OL,7,Fexperience of providing force
OL,8,Fprotection from similar threats,
OL,9,Fhaving deployed ASaC aircraft on
OL,10,Factive operations in the Red Sea last
OL,11,Fyear during the transits of the
OL,12,Fcarrier strike group led by HMS Prince
OL,13,Fof Wales during Operation Highmast.
OL,15,F"This will also compliment the
OL,16,Fdefensive measures provided by the
OL,17,FWildcat aircraft and HMS Dragon, when
OL,18,Fshe arrives in the region, providing a
OL,19,Flayered capability for the protection
OL,20,Fof UK forces."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU|D@NO]
